{"tid":1436262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推俾記者朋友睇！]4點鐘許sir之冇資料解法","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:13:45.000Z","uid":264440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"915227895c25adce5061440cea76a8d8c3a81181","tid":1436262,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"其實佢成日都話冇資料所以唔答<br />\n會唔會有人整理到呢幾日冇資料既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如721 <br />\n問&quot;之前記者會警方話721冇資料，依家已經第xx日，請問有資料未?<br />\n如果仲未有，請問警方情報收集進度係咪有嚴重問題?&quot;之類<br />\n<br />\n而佢將個波射去pprb既話<br />\n就問幾時有pprb記者會<br />\n跟住都估到佢話冇資料ga la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就可以loop番去前面&quot;之前話pprb記者會，依家已經第xx日，請問有資料未?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n每日無限loop loop到佢回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bad4c72deeac2141c555d3a914dfd4b287620e","tid":1436262,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"自推10次睇下有冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b6e74e36086a71f2aaeebe2c641efec04a4373","tid":1436262,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"自推10次睇下有冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14fba29e390785260b4471b4ace36e1f46a7032","tid":1436262,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"自推10次睇下有冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca95495a1f36c66edca42826a5a4f9e87456530b","tid":1436262,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"自推10次睇下有冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee16f3fceb8e1095b69538410212aa2dd980fcbe","tid":1436262,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:06:55.000Z",